Heilbrunn Timeline of Art History: The United States and Canada, 1800–1900 A.D.
Description: Trade cards from the "Photo Gum" series (E184), issued ca. 1889 to promote Photo Gum for Heisel's Gums. Each card depicts an actress photographed in a studio setting.
